        "section_description": "Mad honey can be tempting to your tastebuds, but you should have no more than two spoons a day. The general thumb rule might differ from individual to individual. If you belong somewhere between 18 and 35, you can consume 1 to 2 tablespoons. And if you are 35+, you can stick to 1 tablespoon.",
