        "content_CXHTW7": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Calculate Your Ideal Mad Honey Dose Now",
            "subtitle": "<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-[16px] bg-[#BE935F1A] rounded-3xl p-[16px] pb-[24px] sm:pb-[16px]\">\n        <div class=\"flex sm:flex-col gap-[16px]\">\n          <!-- Tips to Use -->\n          <div class=\"mt-[24px]\">\n            <strong class=\"font-sans text-[18px] font-bold sm:text-[16px] leading-[100%] text-[#020403CC]\">Tips to Use</strong>\n            <div class=\"text-[#000000] text-[16px] sm:text-[14px] font-sans leading-[16px] mt-[6px]\">\n              <ul class=\"text-[#000000] list-disc ml-[1.5em]  tick text-[16px]  sm:text-[14px] font-sans\">\n                <li>Take honey on an empty stomach for better absorption.</li>\n                <li>Mix with warm water or herbal tea for better digestion.</li>\n                <li>\n                  Avoid consuming more than the recommended dosage, especially for Mad Honey due to its psychoactive\n                  effects.\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n\n          <!-- Cautions -->\n          <div class=\"mt-[24px]\">\n            <strong class=\"font-sans  font-bold text-[18px] sm:text-[16px] leading-[100%] text-[#020403CC]\">Cautions</strong>\n            <div class=\"text-[#000000] text-[16px]  sm:text-[14px] font-sans leading-[16px] mt-[6px]\">\n              <ul class=\"text-[#000000] list-disc ml-[1.5em] caution text-[16px]  sm:text-[14px] font-sans\">\n                <li>\n                  Mad Honey should be taken in moderation as over-consumption can lead to dizziness, nausea, or low\n                  blood pressure.\n                </li>\n                <li>Not recommended for pregnant women, children, or people with heart conditions.</li>\n                <li>Consult a healthcare professional before using for medicinal purposes.</li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <!-- Disclaimer -->\n        <div class=\"block py-0 text-[#020403] leading-[110%] \ntext-[16px]  sm:text-[14px] font-sans mt-[6px]\">\n          <strong class=\"text-[18px] sm:text-[16px]  font-bold\">Disclaimer:</strong><br>\n          This calculator provides general recommendations. Consult a healthcare professional for personalized advice,\n          especially if you have underlying health conditions.\n        </div>\n      </div>",
            "description": "<p>Honey is a sweet elixir made by honeybees using the nectar of flowering plants. In the world, there are about 320 different varieties of honey, which vary in color, odor and flavor. Natural Honey contains mostly sugar, as well as a mix of amino acids, vitamins, minerals, iron, zinc and antioxidants. One or two teaspoons a day can truly support your health, just two tablespoons daily can help keep the doctor away! </p><p>A simple way to enjoy <a href=\"/\" title=\"/\">mad honey</a> is by consuming it raw, with one or two tablespoons directly, especially if it's your first time, as it can be potent. We recommended to mix honey into warm water, tea, or smoothies for a unique, beneficial taste. However, if you are new to mad honey, we always recommend starting with smaller amounts, as its potency may be overwhelming.</p><p>Regular honey offers remarkable benefits, too. Try stirring it into warm lemon water, drizzling it over yogurt, or adding it to herbal tea for an immune boost. This everyday superfood is gentle and suitable for the whole family. Honey as a superfood is gentle enough for the entire family and offers a delicious way to enhance well-being.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_text_2": "",
            "button_link_2": ""
          }
        },
